---
title: Rosemary-Fig Grilled Sirloin Steaks with Goat Cheese Salad and Grilled Garlic Bread
description: Agro-dolce deliciousness, on the grill! Sweet, sticky fig and hearty rosemary make a luscious sauce to drizzle over tender grilled sirloin steaks.
